# Claude Code agent memory (machine-local)
.claude/projects/

# FS.GG.SDD — regenerable per-feature readiness output (ADR-0018).
# SDD dogfoods via Spec Kit, so its readiness views land at specs/<id>/readiness/.
# Transient run output: ignore by role, never commit, do not re-include per feature.
# See docs/reference/artifact-taxonomy.md. (Root readiness/ pinned proofs stay committed.)
#
# Exception: the compact merge-boundary verdict is durable-generated (ADR-0026) and IS
# committed. Excluding the directory *contents* (`*/*`) rather than the directory is
# load-bearing: git never descends into an excluded directory, so the negation would
# otherwise be silently inert. Nested agent-commands/<target>/ stays ignored — `*/*`
# matches that directory itself.
specs/*/readiness/*/*
!specs/*/readiness/*/ship-verdict.json
